DRAW FROM 2,1 TO 2,21
DRAW FROM 2,1 TO 6,1
DRAW FROM 6,1 TO 6,80
DRAW FROM 2,80 TO 6,80
DRAW FROM 2,59 TO 2,80
DRAW FROM 1,21 TO 3,59

